**  (KOCD/KONM)
00-CANCEL
11-CHANGE
22-ADD
**  ER
E-01 UPDATE INSTRUCTION IS 0.1.2
E-02 CUSTOMER TPX ISN'T INPUT
E-03 CUSTOMER TPX ISN'T REGISTERED WITH M/F
E-04 ID NO ISN'T INPUT
